      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LESTER RHODE (4) comes off an average run last start when sixth at this track over 390m behind Rocket Roxy (23.58) in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Was in the money prior to that. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has winning claims on his best figures. CAN DO GRACE (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (27.27) in a Bottom Up - Maiden at this track. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. PAW ULA (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fifth (22.90) in a Bottom Up - Maiden at Shepparton latest but did run well two back when in the frame. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. TAKE A SELFIE (8) is worth some thought after placing at this track and distance last start.",
